org.jhove2.module
Interface Command

All Superinterfaces:
Module, Reportable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCommand, AggrefierCommand, AssessorCommand, DigesterCommand, DispatcherCommand, IdentifierCommand
public interface Command
extends Module

Command invoked by JHOVE2 application framework to characterize some aspect of a source unit. Commands are, for most purposes, stateless. The exception is the (except for the metadata members common to all Modules that describe the Module itself). The JHOVE2 framework is configured by plugging a sequence of Command objects into the JHOVE2.commands property.

Author:
smorrissey, slabrams
